====== Notes: ======
  * password in users in DB is kept in SHA1 format.

====== Ideas: ======
  * Suggestion to keep central records of remote access data for plugins, so that it isn't replicated. [TheSkorm]

===== Debian Deps: =====
  * python-pysnmp2
  * python-mysqldb

===== SQL: =====

CREATE DATABASE foonms;
USE foonms;

CREATE TABLE mac(
ipaddress int unsigned,
hostname varchar(1000),
macaddress varchar(20),
portname varchar (30),
date datetime);
